IMPORTANT DISCLAIMER:

This software is designed as a screening and early detection tool for research 
and educational purposes. It is NOT a substitute for professional mental health 
diagnosis or treatment.

Users of this software should:
1. Not rely solely on this tool for mental health assessment
2. Seek professional help for mental health concerns
3. Implement appropriate safeguards and human oversight
4. Comply with all applicable healthcare regulations (HIPAA, GDPR, etc.)
5. Ensure proper data privacy and security measures

The authors and contributors of this software assume no liability for any 
decisions made based on the output of this system. This tool should be used 
as part of a comprehensive mental health support system with appropriate 
professional oversight.

If you are experiencing a mental health crisis, please contact:
- National Suicide Prevention Lifeline: 988 (US)
- Crisis Text Line: Text HOME to 741741 (US)
- International: https://www.befrienders.org/
